    "# ChuckleNet Phase D — Full Redesign\n",
    "\n",
    "**What failed in Phase A-C and why:**\n",
    "\n",
    "| Phase | Approach | Result | Root Cause |\n",
    "|-------|----------|--------|------------|\n",
    "| Phase A | WavLM frozen + MLP | Val F1=0.756, Test F1=0.617 | Frozen encoder = no laughter-specific learning |\n",
    "| Phase B | Gated fusion (XLM-R+WavLM) | Gate→1.0 collapse | Text dominates; frozen audio learns nothing |\n",
    "| Phase B | Biosemiotic LLM features | F1=0.829 ALONE | **Label leakage** — LLM encoded labels in features |\n",
    "| Phase B | Prosody-only (pause/F0/RMS) | F1=0.14 | Word-level aggregation dilutes prosody signal |\n",
    "| Phase B | XLM-R text-only | Test F1=0.819 | Text IS the ceiling for word-level |\n",
    "| Phase C | 3-second windows | Test F1=0.529 | Wrong — model trained on 5s patterns |\n",
    "| Phase C | Threshold sweep (t=0.70) | Test F1=0.574 | Cannot fix precision gap via threshold |\n",
    "\n",
    "**The ONE root cause**: Fully frozen WavLM encoder. XLM-R text (same split) = 0.819. Frozen audio = 0.617. Same windowing, same splits, only difference = encoder frozen vs unfrozen.\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## Phase D: Redesigned Architecture\n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    "Audio → WavLM → [Attention Pooling] → [Engram Compression] → 128-dim\n",
    "         ↑ (partial unfreeze, last 6 layers, lr=5e-5)\n",
    "         \n",
    "Text  → XLM-R  → mean_pool(768) → linear(768→256) → 256-dim\n",
    "         (frozen, just for embeddings)\n",
    "\n",
    "Prosody → prosody_proj(52→64) → 64-dim (extracted from raw audio)\n",
    "\n",
    "Fused: concat([text_256, audio_128, prosody_64]) → MLP(448→256→128→2)\n",
    "       ↑ concat fusion, NO gate (gate collapsed in prior attempts)\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "**Key improvements over Phase A-C:**\n",
    "1. `AttentionPooling` instead of `MeanPooling` — learns which audio frames matter\n",
    "2. `EngramModule` — information bottleneck forcing dense laughter encoding\n",
    "3. Partial unfreeze (last 6 layers, discriminative LR decay)\n",
    "4. Concat fusion (NO learnable gate — gates collapsed to text-only in 3 attempts)\n",
    "5. Prosody extracted at word-level WITHIN the 5s window, not utterance-aggregated"
   ]
  },
